<main class="flex flex-col flex-1 justify-center items-center gap-8">
  <section class="space-y-4 max-w-[36ch] text-center *:text-pretty">
    <h1 class="mb-8 font-display text-3xl">Welcome to Counterspell Games</h1>

    <p>
      We're bringing the magic of Table-Top RPGs to beginners though our guided, in-person &amp; <abbr title="in real life">irl</abbr> events.
    </p>

    <p>
      If you've always wanted to play a game like <a title="Dungeons & Dragons" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dungeons_%26_Dragons">D&amp;D</a> or <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Daggerheart">Daggerheart</a>, but never had the time, the place, or a guide to light the way, now is your moment.
    </p>

    <p class="font-bold">There is a place at our table for all!</p>
  </section>

  <ul class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 my-6 *:max-w-[3in] text-sm text-left">
    <li class="bg-white shadow px-2 md:px-4 py-4 md:py-6 border border-black/10 rounded-sm -rotate-1 md:-rotate-2 md:translate-y-2">
      <i class="mb-4 text-emerald-600 fa-scroll-old fa-regular fa-duotone"></i>
      <h3 class="mb-1 font-bold text-emerald-600 text-xl">One story. One sitting.</h3>
      <p>Each game session is a self-contained story arc that unfolds across one afternoon. Your actions will shape the world, so no two are alike. <em>What will be your next adventure?</em></p>
    </li>

    <li class="bg-white shadow px-2 md:px-4 py-4 md:py-6 border border-black/10 rounded-sm rotate-1 md:-rotate-1">
      <i class="mb-4 text-pink-700 fa-regular fa-duotone fa-swords"></i>
      <h3 class="mb-1 font-bold text-pink-700 text-xl">Choose your hero.</h3>
      <p>Our playable characters come complete with deep backstories, signature equipment & weapons, and unique abilities. <em>Their destiny is in your hands!</em></p>
    </li>

    <li class="bg-white shadow px-2 md:px-4 py-4 md:py-6 border border-black/10 rounded-sm -rotate-1 md:rotate-1">
      <i class="mb-4 text-purple-700 fa-regular fa-duotone fa-planet-ringed"></i>
      <h3 class="mb-1 font-bold text-purple-700 text-xl">Enter the Rift.</h3>
      <p>From space fairing mages to garden moons, musical weaponry and ancestry woven as scarves, The Rift is a place of endless possibilities. <em>What will you discover?</em></p>
    </li>

    <li class="bg-white shadow px-2 md:px-4 py-4 md:py-6 border border-black/10 rounded-sm rotate-1 md:rotate-2 md:translate-y-2">
      <i class="mb-4 text-sky-700 fa-regular fa-duotone fa-dice"></i>
      <h3 class="mb-1 font-bold text-sky-700 text-xl">Play together, for real.</h3>
      <p>Counterspell events are completely in person. Take a break from notifications, meet new people, and share a creative experience. <em>No screens, no stress.</em></p>
    </li>
  </ul>


    <scection class="space-y-6 text-center">
      <p class="text-xl text-center">The Rift awaits. What will be <em>your</em> story?</p>

      <%= form_with url: session_path, class: "space-y-2" do |form| %>
        <%= hashcash_hidden_field_tag %>

        <%= form.email_field :email,
          required: true,
          placeholder: "Enter your email address",
          class: "text-center fun-interaction"
        %>

        <label for="agree_to_terms" class="flex justify-center items-center gap-2 font-light italic">
          <%= checkbox_tag :agree_to_terms, "yes", true, required: true, class: "accent-purple-700 size-4" %>
          <span>I agree to Counterspellâ€™s <%= link_to "Privacy Policy", page_path("privacy-policy") %>.</span>
        </label>

        <%= form.submit "Start your Journey", class: "btn mt-4" %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>

<%= javascript_include_tag "hashcash", defer: true %>